ACTION VIEW METHODS:-

1) FORM
a) form_for:- takes an object and helps us to build an html form
b) text_field:- to give an input area(one-line)
c) text_area:- multiple line
d) check_box:- generally used when attribute type is boolean
e)submit:- to sumbit the query
f)date:-
g)date_select:-
h)collection_select:- takes 4 arguments(attribute, data-source, primary-key, the column names to be displayed as values in dropdown) takes option 'prompt'
it is always used on a attribute which will be a foreign key reference
